      • EditorCell_Error

        public EditorCell_Error​(EditorContext editorContext,
                        org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SNode node,
                        String errorText,
                        boolean editable)
        Parameters:
        editable - - there are two different kinds of CEll_Error in MPS: - one (!editable) intended to show error text and then substitute it completely then user type something e.g. list<|> - another (editable) allows editing error text directly without replacing it with first types character e.g. myVariable.|field - in case "field" is not resolved, it should be highlighted as error, but should be still completely editable
